 <name>Scatola</name>
 <_summary>File manager for the GDE2 desktop environment</_summary>
 <_description>
  <p>
   Scatola is the official file manager for the GDE2 desktop. It allows for
   browsing directories, as well as previewing files and launching applications
   associated with them. It is also responsible for handling the icons on
   the GDE2 desktop. It works on local and remote file systems.
  </p>
  <p>
   Scatola is extensible through a plugin system, similar to that of GNOME Nautilus,
   of which Scatola is a fork.
  </p>
 </_description>
